---
const brand = "JaiSellers Companies";
const title = "Systems Framework";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{title} — {brand}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A simple framework for building governance, revenue, and narrative systems that last." />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/site.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="topbar">
      <a class="logo" href="/">{brand}</a>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/consulting">Consulting (JSC)</a>
        <a href="/design">Design</a>
        <a href="/jsi">JSI</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/blog">Notes</a>
        <a class="nav-cta" href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="kicker">Framework</p>
          <h1>Vision → Structure → Sustain</h1>
          <p style="margin-top:14px; max-width:76ch;">
            We build in a predictable order so organizations don’t collapse under stress: clarity first, then governance,
            then funding systems, then narrative execution.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section section-alt">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>The three layers</h2>
          <div class="grid3" style="margin-top:18px;">
            <article class="card">
              <h3>1) Governance</h3>
              <p>Roles, policies, decision-making, board ops, compliance rhythm.</p>
              <ul class="bullets">
                <li>Bylaws + policies</li>
                <li>Board cadence + packets</li>
                <li>Risk controls</li>
              </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="card">
              <h3>2) Revenue</h3>
              <p>Budget architecture + grant readiness + pipeline + reporting.</p>
              <ul class="bullets">
                <li>Program budgets</li>
                <li>Grant calendar</li>
                <li>Reporting system</li>
              </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="card">
              <h3>3) Narrative</h3>
              <p>Messaging and brand assets aligned to what you can truly deliver.</p>
              <ul class="bullets">
                <li>Case for support</li>
                <li>Homepage copy</li>
                <li>Campaign templates</li>
              </ul>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="container split">
          <div>
            <h2>What you get</h2>
            <p style="margin-top:10px; max-width:70ch;">
              Not just advice. We deliver templates, checklists, trackers, and a maintenance rhythm your team can run.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="callout">
            <h3>Start with structure</h3>
            <p style="margin-top:10px;">If you’re unsure what’s next, start with a consult.</p>
            <a class="btn primary" href="/contact" style="margin-top:12px;">Book</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} {brand}</span>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
